# Canonical identity for this repository.
#
# Every commit here is authored by old8man; three different e-mail addresses
# were used over time (a global git config leaked `luxquant@gst.st` for a
# handful of 2026-04-26 / 2026-06-01 commits, and `taaliman@protonmail.com`
# for a few later ones). This file maps them all onto the canonical address
# so `git log`, `git shortlog -sne`, `git blame` and friends show one author.
#
# NOTE: .mailmap fixes git's own tooling. GitHub's web attribution instead
# maps a commit's raw e-mail to whichever account has verified it, so to make
# the historical commits show as old8man there, add `luxquant@gst.st` and
# `taaliman@protonmail.com` as verified e-mails on the old8man GitHub account
# (Settings -> Emails). That needs no history rewrite.
old8man <oldman@gst.st> <luxquant@gst.st>
old8man <oldman@gst.st> <taaliman@protonmail.com>
old8man <oldman@gst.st> <oldman@gst.st>
